>- ASRock Polychrome SYNC*<br/>UEFI<br/>- ASRock EZ Mode<br/>- ASRock Full HD UEFI<br/>- ASRock My Favorites in UEFI<br/>- ASRock Auto Driver Installer<br/>- ASRock Instant Flash<br/>- ASRock Easy RAID Installer</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">*These utilities can be downloaded from ASRock Live Update &amp; APP Shop.</span></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>Accessories</strong></span></p><ol></ol></td><td><span style=\"font-size:16px\">- 1 x User Manual<br/>- 2 x SATA Data Cables<br/>- 3 x Screws for M.2 Sockets<br/>- 1 x Standoff for M.2 Socket</span></td></tr><tr><td><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>Form Factor</strong></span></td><td><span style=\"font-size:16px\">- Micro ATX Form Factor: 9.6-in x 9.6-in, 24.4 cm x 24.4 cm</span></td></tr><tr><td><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>OS</strong></span></td><td><p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">- Microsoft® Windows® 10 64-bit / 11 64-bit</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size:16px\">*Windows® 10 only supports version 21H2 or later</span></p></td></tr><tr><td><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><strong>Certifications</strong></span></td><td><span style=\"font-size:16px\">- FCC, CE<br/>- ErP/EuP ready (ErP/EuP ready power supply is required)</span></td></tr></tbody></table><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"//file.hstatic.net/1000361104/file/1_b4fdce1ad2974caba213e1ff95439384_master.png\"/><img src=\"//file.hstatic.net/1000361104/file/2_0cb0f3425c414cf8a0ea4804f26d358d_master.png\"/><img src=\"//file.hstatic.net/1000361104/file/3_0d3c714af35c4b8ab9db2733d0f96ab3_master.png\"/><img src=\"//file.hstatic.net/1000361104/file/5_0061f40061824b89acf89b5aaf2e2868_master.png\"/><img src=\"//file.hstatic.net/1000361104/file/6_e2d9722796cb4eda87c410b2dffff77a_master.png\"/><img src=\"//file.hstatic.net/1000361104/file/7_a5492d8d79484c06a910ba6c1a09a90f_master.png\"/><img src=\"//file.hstatic.net/1000361104/file/8_7aa7778e8a0648828139b0c84a84cde7_master.png\"/><img src=\"//file.h